					ticua
				</h1>

				<section
					class="card dc-card p-7 mb-2 border border-border-subtle w-full max-w-sm mx-auto text-left"
					id="discordCard"
				>
					<div
						class="dc-loading text-text-secondary text-xs italic mb-2 animate-pulse"
